description: An illustration of a photo booth: the body of the photo booth is mostly a bright red with a pale yellow strip along the top of the front; there are also thick silver lines outlining various parts of the photo booth. A gray curtain covers the top half of the entrance of the photo booth and the bench inside is red. There is a pale yellow screen to the left of the entrance and a small rectangular slot below it where a photo strip is dispensed.
